
Styrsignaler:

uPC
    000     +1
    001     op addr
    010     A a-mod addr
    011     B a-mod addr
    100     jmp
    101     jmp on Z
    111     0

PC
    0       PC (nothing)
    1       +1

3x minne
    2bit
        read
        write
        nothing

graphic
    1 bit (0 bit?)
        reset (sätt neutral färg när vi rensar minnet, kanske kan ledas till `not (P1 or P2)` om vi ej rensar status före)

buss in
    4bit
        PC
        M1
        M2
        OP
        AR A
        AR B
        FIFO
        I/O

buss out
    4bit
        PC
        M1
        M2
        OP
        ALU A
        ALU B
        IR
        ADR
        FIFO
        I/O
        nothing


uCount
    2 bit
        0
        +1
        update Z

ADR
    3 bit select from
        M1
        M2
        AR A
        AR B
        PC
        buss
        nothing

ALU (both)
    3bit control function
        -1
        +1
        load
        add
        sub
        cmp
        nothing

ALU A
    2 bit select input
        M1
        M2
        PC
        buss

ALU B
    2 bit select input
        M1
        M2
        PC
        buss

FIFO
    2bit
        read
        write
        nothing

    3 bit P1 function
        incr read
        zero read
        incr write
        zero write
        nothing

    3 bit P2 function
        incr read
        zero read
        incr write
        zero write
        nothing

    1bit
        change player
        nothing

M1
    3 bit choose in
        AR A
        AR B
        M2
        buss
        nothing

M2
    3 bit choose in
        AR A
        AR B
        M1
        buss
        nothing

Totalt
    2 rw OP mem
    2 rw op1 mem
    2 rw op1 mem
    4 buss in
    4 buss out
    3 uPC
    2 uCount
    1 PC
    3 ADR
    3 ALU (both)
    2 ALU A input
    2 ALU B input
    7 FIFO
    3 M1
    3 M2

    43 styrsignaler

    + 8 bit hoppaddress

    51 bit

